						<p><div class="item">
<h2><a class="listing" style="link" href="/en/Dossiers/CTA-and-S-T/Selected-publications/SRI-much-more-than-more-rice2" title="SRI: much more than more rice" alt="link">SRI: much more than more rice</a></h2>

	
					<p>The March 2013 issue of Farming Matters is dedicated to the System of Rice Intensification (SRI). It contains case studies, analysis and interviews dedicated to this innovative form of rice production.<a href="http://www.agriculturesnetwork.org/get-involved/events/events-2013/sri-wageningen" target="_self">http://www.agriculturesnetwork.org/get-involved/events/events-2013/sri-wageningen</a>(Farming Matters, 03/2013)</p>
							<p><span class="date">22/05/2013</span></p>
	<div class="cnt">
	<a class="link" href="/en/Dossiers/CTA-and-S-T/Selected-publications/SRI-much-more-than-more-rice2">Read more...</a>
