<h2><a class="listing" style="link" href="/en/Dossiers/CTA-and-S-T/Selected-publications/Genetics-in-agriculture" title="Genetics in agriculture" alt="link">Genetics in agriculture</a></h2>

	
					<p>In this issue of GeneWatch: livestock genebanks, agricultural biotechnology policy, patented seeds, agricultural technologies in a warming world, and more.<a href="http://goo.gl/0qehY" target="_self">http://goo.gl/0qehY</a>(Council for Responsible Genetics, Jan-Mar 2013)</p>
							<p><span class="date">22/05/2013</span></p>
