						<p><div class="item">
<h2><a class="listing" style="link" href="/en/Dossiers/CTA-and-S-T/Selected-publications/Guidelines-access-and-benefit-sharing-in-research-projects" title="Guidelines: access and benefit sharing in research projects" alt="link">Guidelines: access and benefit sharing in research projects</a></h2>

	
					<p>These guidelines describe the type of agreements that can be used in access and benefit sharing in research projects. Target audience are scientists working with crop genetic resources and related traditional knowledge.<a href="http://agrobiodiversityplatform.org/par/2013/04/12/guidelines-access-and-benefit-sharing-in-research-projects/" target="_self">http://agrobiodiversityplatform.org/par/2013/04/12/guidelines-access-and-benefit-sharing-in-research-projects/</a>(PAR, 12/04/2013)</p>
