						<p><div class="item">
<h2><a class="listing" style="link" href="/en/Dossiers/CTA-and-S-T/Selected-publications/Opportunities-and-limitations-for-functional-agrobiodiversity-FAB-in-the-European-context" title="Opportunities and limitations for functional agrobiodiversity (FAB) in the European context" alt="link">Opportunities and limitations for functional agrobiodiversity (FAB) in the European context</a></h2>

	
					<p>Reforms in EU policy facilitate the implementation of FAB concepts in agriculture but Impediments to the adoption of FAB approaches still exist, mainly: no ready-to-use management practices and lack of data on the effectiveness of FAB measures.<a href="http://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S1462901112002523" target="_self">http://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S1462901112002523</a>(via ELN-FAB Newsletter, April 2013)</p>
							<p><span class="date">22/05/2013</span></p>
	<div class="cnt">
	<a class="link" href="/en/Dossiers/CTA-and-S-T/Selected-publications/Opportunities-and-limitations-for-functional-agrobiodiversity-FAB-in-the-European-context">Read more...</a>
